00:30:31.940 --> 00:30:34.150
AUDIENCE: Thank
you, first of all.

00:30:34.150 --> 00:30:41.200
I think I saw a study
recently that correlated

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:48.210
a person's actual health with
the empathy of their caregiver.

00:30:48.210 --> 00:30:49.550
Am I getting this right?

00:30:49.550 --> 00:30:50.341
KATE GRANGER: Yeah.

00:30:50.341 --> 00:30:52.616
AUDIENCE: So did you start that?

00:30:52.616 --> 00:30:55.860
KATE GRANGER: I didn't,
but that study-- there's

00:30:55.860 --> 00:30:59.510
several studies out there, that
the better the relationship you

00:30:59.510 --> 00:31:01.660
have with your
health care provider,

00:31:01.660 --> 00:31:03.440
the better your outcome.

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:07.000
And it's been repeated in
sort of surgical settings,

00:31:07.000 --> 00:31:09.580
in cancer settings.

00:31:09.580 --> 00:31:13.180
And I think that's why this
is so important, that we've

00:31:13.180 --> 00:31:16.190
got to start those
relationships and consider

00:31:16.190 --> 00:31:19.620
those relationships as
therapeutic in themselves.

00:31:19.620 --> 00:31:24.240
That whatever the treatments
we give, or the surgeries or we

00:31:24.240 --> 00:31:26.800
do, or whatever we do as
health care professionals,

00:31:26.800 --> 00:31:29.380
we have to think
of the relationship

00:31:29.380 --> 00:31:33.480
we have with our patients as
kind of the first building

00:31:33.480 --> 00:31:35.910
block of whatever
we're going to do.

00:31:35.910 --> 00:31:37.670
Because if you
think about it, you

00:31:37.670 --> 00:31:40.760
are going to comply with what
your doctor recommends more

00:31:40.760 --> 00:31:44.310
if you trust them and you
believe in what they're saying,

00:31:44.310 --> 00:31:47.230
and you've worked together
and collaborated on whatever

00:31:47.230 --> 00:31:48.890
the treatment plan is.

00:31:48.890 --> 00:31:50.940
So I think that's probably
why the outcomes are

00:31:50.940 --> 00:31:53.490
better for people who
have better relationships.

00:31:53.490 --> 00:31:55.120
And you build
better relationships

00:31:55.120 --> 00:31:56.910
if you're more empathic.

00:31:56.910 --> 00:31:59.660
AUDIENCE: I know that you've
