00:32:06.840 --> 00:32:09.220
between where you were
in the US and the UK

00:32:09.220 --> 00:32:14.410
with regard to introductions
and being patient centered?

00:32:14.410 --> 00:32:16.220
KATE GRANGER: So
obviously, my experience

00:32:16.220 --> 00:32:20.690
