00:32:24.270 --> 00:32:27.020
for you than they do in the UK.

00:32:29.960 --> 00:32:35.530
And the doctors were kind
of a bit more distant.

00:32:35.530 --> 00:32:38.080
So the relationship
that you have

00:32:38.080 --> 00:32:40.890
with your nurse when you're
in inpatient in the US

00:32:40.890 --> 00:32:42.500
seems to be really important.

00:32:42.500 --> 00:32:46.330
That seems to be the central
thing that's going on.

00:32:46.330 --> 00:32:49.410
And the doctors are just
kind of on the periphery

00:32:49.410 --> 00:32:51.330
doing the orders
